<F P=100> SOUTH ASIA </F>
<F P=101> Afghanistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hekmatyar Faction Not To Lift Kabul Blockade </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2202111394 Tripoli JANA in English 0806 GMT 22 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2202111394 </F>
<F P=104>  Tripoli JANA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An-Nawar [Feb] 22, JAMAHIRIYAH NEWS AGENCY -- The 
faction of Golboddin Hekmatyar which presently surrounds the 
Afghanistan capital Kabul has announced that it will not lift 
its blockade which denies the city any relief supplies. The 
faction was able to intensify its blockade within the pattern of 
stuggle for power between what were once called mojahedin and 
later became political rivals whose conflict is systematically 
destroying the country. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

