<F P=102>  LD2002184794 Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network in Pashto 1530 
GMT 20 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2002184794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Pashto </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An offensive by the notorious Dostam militia, which 
was mounted this morning in western Konduz Province, was 
defeated. 
  A military correspondent of the Bakhtar Information Agency 
reports that the infamous Dostam militia, in cooperation with 
communist generals, early this morning mounted an offensive in 
Konduz Province's western areas that was completely foiled as a 
result of the courage shown by the Islamic army and mojahedin of 
the Konduz Province. Some [words indistinct] of the criminal 
militia of Dostam. 
  The report adds that all mojahedin of Knoduz Province, in 
united ranks, are continuing jihad against the notorious 
militia. Mop-up operations in Konduz Province's districts are 
continuing by the mojahedin and the faithful local people. 

</TEXT>

