Intelligence Department, the Public Security Department, and the 
Civil Defense Department; the chief of staff of the Royal Ground 
Forces; the mayor of Amman; the governor of Amman; and several 
senior civilian and military officials. 
  His excellency the guest reviewed the guard of honor and was 
accorded an official sendoff at Queen Alia Airport. Leaving 
with him was Dr. Yasin Sa'id Nu'man, head of the secretariat of 
the office of the Yemeni Socialist Party's Central Committee. 

