  [Text] AKHIR KHABAR has learned that the security organs 
yesterday arrested an Islamist in connection with the recent 
explosions. Some sources said he belongs to the Islamic Action 
Front [IAF], but IAF sources denied that. 
  According to informed sources, the new arrest raises the 
number of detainees to over 50. The competent authorities, 
however, are expected to release about 13 other detainees who 
were arrested for interrogation but were found not guilty. 
