<H3> <TI>   Gaps in Security Talks `Unbridgeable' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2202192894 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network in 
Hebrew 1800 GMT 22 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2202192894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network </F>


