<F P=102>  NC1902181394 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 19 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1902181394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Four radical members of the PLO Executive Committee 
have pledged to prevent the implementation of the 
Palestinian-Israeli Cairo agreement, saying it is a catastrophe 
for the Palestinians and involves very serious concessions. 
  The four Palestinian officials are: 'Abd-al-Rahim Malluh, 
member of the Popular Front for the Liberation of Palestine; 
Taysir Khalid, member of the Democratic Front for the Liberation 
of Palestine; Mahmud Isma'il, member of the Arab Liberation 
Front; and 'Abdallah Hurani, an independent Executive Committee 
member. 

