<H3> <TI>   Clashes Reported Between North, South; Reaction Noted </TI></H3>
<H4>   Ambush Reported 22 Feb </H4>
<F P=102> NC2202180394 Paris AFP in English 1754 GMT 22 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2202180394 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>


<TEXT>
