Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Amman, Feb 22 (AFP)--Northern Yemeni troops on 
Tuesday ambushed and killed 15 soldiers from the rival south, a 
Yemeni official said here. 
  The ambush was sprung by a northern brigade at al-'Amaliqah, 
based in the Abyan region of southern Yemen, the south Yemeni 
official said in Jordan where the rival leaders signed a 
reconciliation accord on Sunday. 
  There was no confirmation from the north. 

</TEXT>

