Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The president of the Republic, Lieutenant General 
'Umar al-Bashir, on Monday issued the 10th Republican Decree for 
1994, appointing 142 ministers and advisers for the 26 states of 
the country. According to the decree, every northern state is 
