<H3> <TI>   Pakistani Foreign Minister Arrives in Kabul </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2302182694 Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network in Dari 1600 
GMT 23 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2302182694 </F>
