  [Text] Prime Minister Dr. 'Abd-al-Salam al-Majali received 
in his office at the Prime Ministry this morning Mahmud Muhammad 
Mahmud, Egyptian minister of economy and foreign trade. Dr. 
Rima Khalaf, Jordanian minister of industry and trade, and the 
Egyptian ambassador in Amman attended the meeting. Talks dealt 
with ways to boost and upgrade cooperation between the two 
