<F P=102>  JN2402091894 Baghdad INA in Arabic 0815 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN2402091894 </F>
<F P=104>  Baghdad INA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Baghdad, 24 Feb (INA)--Staff Lieutenant General 
Ahmad Ibrahim Hammash, assistant to the chief of staff of the 
army for administration, has denied imperialist and Zionist 
propaganda about drafting reserves or disbanding others who have 
completed their compulsory service. 
  In a statement to AL-QADISIYAH published today, the 
assistant 
to the chief of staff said those conscripts born in 1973 and who 
