<H3> <TI>   Spokesman Condemns Attack on Israeli Women </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2402103894 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 2200 GMT 
23 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2402103894 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>


