GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2402201594 </F>
<F P=104>  Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Pashto </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The infamous militia of the fiendish triangle today 
mounted a failed attack in Kondoz in which they, at the blessing 
of God and the battle of the Islamic Army, suffered a heavy 
defeat and extensive losses. The infamous militia, who attacked 
the area of Qotailich and kidnapped several people, faced the 
fatal blows of the ambush units of Corp No. 6, Brigade 54, and 
mechanized forces. The Islamic Army of Afghanistan entered the 
region and inflicted heavy losses on the militia. As a result 
of the blows, three pieces of mortar, three pieces of 82-mm 
artillery, 80 Kalashnikovs, 10 pieces of RPG8 and [words 
indistinct] desert artillery, and a ZK1 machinegun of the enemy 
have been captured by the Islamic Army of Afghanistan. [Word 
indistinct] of the invaders were captured, and 15 others, 
including two generals by the names of Gholam Rasul and 
(?Mohammad) Saleh, were killed. As a result of the 
counteroffensive and the heroism and bravery of the Islamic Army 
of Afghanistan, the areas of [words indistinct] were cleared of 
the militia. 

