<H3> <TI>   `Security Sources' Warn Against Firing in South </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2402124494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 1030 
GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2402124494 </F>
<F P=104>  Kafr Killa Voice of the South </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Citing security sources in the border zone, our 
military correspondent reports that the Lebanese Army has 
recently allowed firing in areas under its control or areas 
adjacent to its deployment zone. The security sources affirmed 
to our correspondent that any shooting directed at us will be 
returned, and this will expose the Lebanese Army troops to the 
possibility of being hit. The sources added that the Lebanese 
Army must take this into consideration. 

</TEXT>

