  [Text] Demonstrations have been staged in a number of 
Yemeni cities to protest the armed attacks on the population of 
Mudiyah in the valiant Abyan Governorate. Raised placards 
called for an end to the armed aggression and continuing attacks 
on the population. They also called for the military units to 
